OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government is bracing itself
OL,7,Ffor reaction to its revised
OL,8,FSustainable Farming Scheme.
OL,10,FPlans for the scheme, which is
OL,11,Fdesigned to replace the funding for
OL,12,FWelsh farmers previously given by the
OL,13,FEuropean Union, first began after
OL,14,FBrexit. But despite several
OL,15,Fconsultations and draft proposals, it
OL,16,Fhas been mired in controversy.
