OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FLater today the Deputy First Minister
OL,7,FHuw Irranca-Davies MS, who has
OL,8,Fresponsibility for Climate Change and
OL,9,FRural Affairs, will outline the policy
OL,10,Fto the Senedd.
OL,12,FHe and other ministers will now be
OL,13,Feagerly awaiting the reaction of Welsh
OL,14,Ffarmers and environmental groups to
OL,15,Fthe controversial subsidy scheme.
OL,17,FLast year, widespread protests broke
OL,18,Fout across Wales when a previous
OL,19,Fproposal said that farmers had to have
OL,20,F10% of their land covered in trees to
OL,21,Faccess any money.
