OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government's own impact
OL,7,Fassessment on that draft proposal
OL,8,Fsuggested that there could be
OL,9,Fthousands of job losses in the
OL,10,Fagricultural industry. In May 2024,
OL,11,FHuw Irranca-Davies MS was appointed as
OL,12,Fthe new Climate Change and Rural
OL,13,FAffairs Secretary and "paused" the
OL,14,Fscheme.
OL,16,FSince then, he has held a series of
OL,17,F"roundtable" discussions with farmers
OL,18,Fand environmental groups to try and
OL,19,Ffind a way forward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/17
