OL,6,FToday that new scheme will be outlined
OL,7,Fto Senedd members, but it could be met
OL,8,Fwith criticism from farming unions and
OL,9,Fenvironmental charities.
OL,11,FThe Minister says it's a "scheme for
OL,12,Fthe whole of Wales - a whole farm,
OL,13,Fwhole nation approach".
