OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FHe said: "This Scheme is the product
OL,7,Fof extensive collaboration. We've
OL,8,Flistened carefully to farmers across
OL,9,FWales and revised our approach to
OL,10,Fensure it works for the agricultural
OL,11,Findustry and meets our shared
OL,12,Fresponsibilities to the natural world
OL,13,Faround us.
OL,15,F"I would like to thank those who
OL,16,Fresponded to consultations and
OL,17,Fattended meetings the length and
OL,18,Fbreadth of Wales, and I'm grateful to
OL,19,Fall members of the Ministerial
OL,20,FRoundtable and supporting Working
OL,21,FGroups for their input.
