OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FBut today environmental charities like
OL,7,FWWF Cymru will say that it "falls far
OL,8,Fshort of what is needed to put Welsh
OL,9,Ffarming on a sustainable footing."
OL,10,FAlexander Phillips, Policy and
OL,11,FAdvocacy Manager at the charity, says
OL,12,Fthat it's a "missed opportunity".
OL,14,F"It appears that today's Sustainable
OL,15,FFarming Scheme is now sustainable in
OL,16,Fname only. The overall framework has
OL,17,Fpromise and should be supported and
OL,18,Fimproved.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
