OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,F"Nonetheless, today's proposals for
OL,7,Fthe first year fall far short of
OL,8,Fwhat's needed to deliver change
OL,9,Fquickly, and in part risks recreating
OL,10,Fbits of the old schemes with
OL,11,Fexaggerated area-based payment rates
OL,12,Ffor little apparent public good."
