OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,F"The transformation promised has not
OL,7,Fyet materialised, and we now risk a
OL,8,Fcontinuation of the status quo which
OL,9,Fcould see jobs and farm numbers
OL,10,Fcontinue to decline, extreme weather
OL,11,Fconditions making farms and
OL,12,Fcommunities more vulnerable, rising
OL,13,Femissions, and unsustainable practices
OL,14,Fcontinuing to cause biodiversity loss
OL,15,Fand river pollution."
OL,17,FThe Scheme is also likely to draw
OL,18,Fplenty of political reaction when it
OL,19,Fis outlined in the Senedd this
OL,20,Fafternoon.
