OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FThe Welsh Conservatives have already
OL,7,Fsaid that the scheme should be put to
OL,8,Fa binding vote in the Senedd, and
OL,9,Ftomorrow that motion will be debated
OL,10,Fin the Senedd chamber.
OL,12,FWelsh Conservative Shadow Secretary
OL,13,Ffor Economy, Energy and Rural Affairs
OL,14,FSam Kurtz MS says that a vote is
OL,15,F"vital".
OL,17,F"Agriculture is vital to the Welsh
OL,18,Feconomy, culture and language, and
OL,19,Ffarmers need clear answers to plan for
OL,20,Ftheir future, their livelihoods, and
OL,21,Ftheir communities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/17
