OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,F"It's only right that the Welsh Labour
OL,7,FGovernment's Sustainable Farming
OL,8,FScheme is put to a final Senedd vote,
OL,9,Fto ensure democratic legitimacy, and
OL,10,Fthe confidence of the agricultural
OL,11,Fsector."
OL,13,FMeanwhile Plaid Cymru has said that
OL,14,Fany scheme must be "workable" for
OL,15,Ffarmers.
