OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FLlyr Gruffydd, the shadow Rural
OL,7,FAffairs Secretary, said: "Plaid Cymru
OL,8,Fhas previously called for a reduction
OL,9,Fin the number of Universal Actions
OL,10,Fwithin the scheme, greater flexibility
OL,11,Fon tree planting including scrapping
OL,12,Fthe 10% target, and more emphasis on
OL,13,Fthe social value of farming as a
OL,14,Fpublic good.
OL,16,F"We also previously secured a longer
OL,17,Ftransitional period between the BPS
OL,18,Fand the SFS and we would urge the
OL,19,FGovernment to avoid any kind of
OL,20,Ffunding cliff edge as we move from one
OL,21,Fsystem to the other.
