OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,F"We also hope that the Cabinet
OL,7,FSecretary will commit to long-term
OL,8,Ffunding for the scheme."
OL,10,FThe most controversial part of the
OL,11,Frevised Scheme may no longer centre
OL,12,Faround any requirement to plant trees,
OL,13,Fbut could revolve around the
OL,14,Ftransition from the status quo to the
OL,15,Fnew policy.
