OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FAt a media briefing yesterday
OL,7,Fafternoon, Welsh Government officials
OL,8,Fconfirmed that from the 1 January
OL,9,F2026, the current scheme that farmers
OL,10,Freceive funding from will be worth
OL,11,Fjust 60% of its current value. That
OL,12,Fmeans that if farmers want to receive
OL,13,Fmore money from the Welsh Government,
OL,14,Fthey will have to sign up to the
OL,15,FSustainable Farming Scheme next year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/17
