OL,3,CFarming subsidy: Welsh Government
OL,4,Cbraced for reaction to revised scheme
OL,6,FThe current scheme - the so-called
OL,7,FBasic Payment Scheme - is expected to
OL,8,Fbe phased out by 2029. Welsh farmers
OL,9,Fknew that a transition phase was
OL,10,Fproposed. But because of the delay in
OL,11,Fimplementing the scheme, they may have
OL,12,Fhoped that the current funding model
OL,13,Fwould retain 80% of its current value
OL,14,Fnext year.
OL,16,FThis announcement is likely to attract
OL,17,Fplenty of debate and reaction later
OL,18,Ftoday.
